title: GoPro: Daily Doubles With Mikey Taylor and Mike Mo
description:
Shot 100% on the HD HERO3+® camera from http://GoPro.com.

Mikey Taylor and Mike Mo Capaldi demonstrate the "throw-pro" camera move as they shred the infamous Albertson Ledges. 

Throw-pro: An in motion hand-off or toss of a GoPro camera to another subject who then turns the camera back onto the thrower and films them.


Music
Factor "Club Soda O G"
